Title of your Project/program:
moving hearts like bubble

what is the goal of your project?
this project is created to produce an animated visualization where heart shapes will move around the screen like floating bubbles. It is fun and visually appealing effect that can be
used for creative purposes for example for valentine's day, animations, greeting cards and so on, or even for learning graphical programming with python.

hpw to run your code?
first you need to install python in your computer, then run the script as moving_hearts.py. Finally enjoy the animation like bubbles on your screen.
